Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user6@test.com",
    "password": "password1"
}

### 토큰갱신
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{refreshToken}}

### 내 정보 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 내 정보 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

